"title": "8493: watchfulness, of believers",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8493: watchfulness, of believers",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Alertness to dangers and blessings in the Christian life, and also to opportunities to do good.</p>\n<h2>Watchfulness for dangers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:8\">1PE 5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:23\">PRO 4:23</a></p>\n<h3>The danger of false teaching</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:15\">MAT 7:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:8\">PSA 94:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:33-Prov8:34\">PRO 8:33–8:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:4-Matt24:5\">MAT 24:4–24:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:15\">MRK 8:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:17\">ROM 16:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:13\">1CO 16:13</a></p>\n<h3>The danger of temptation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:41\">MAT 26:41</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:38\">MRK 14:38</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:15\">DEU 4:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:4\">1KI 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:15\">LUK 12:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:1-Luke17:3\">LUK 17:1–17:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:12\">1CO 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:1\">GAL 6:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:8\">2JN 1:8</a></p>\n<h3>The danger of neglecting the word of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:9\">DEU 4:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:5\">JOS 22:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:3\">1KI 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:1\">HEB 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:25\">HEB 12:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:19\">2PE 1:19</a></p>\n<h3>The danger of damage to the Lord's work</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:9\">NEH 4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:3\">NEH 7:3</a></p>\n<h3>The danger of speaking sinfully</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:1\">PSA 39:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps141:3\">PSA 141:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:3\">PRO 13:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:23\">PRO 21:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:26\">JAS 1:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:5-Jas3:8\">JAS 3:5–3:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:10\">1PE 3:10</a></p>\n<h2>Watchfulness for blessings</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:15\">PSA 25:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:9\">PSA 59:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps123:1-Ps123:2\">PSA 123:1–123:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps130:5-Ps130:6\">PSA 130:5–130:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:9\">ISA 40:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:7\">MIC 7:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:25\">LUK 2:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:36-Luke2:38\">LUK 2:36–2:38</a></p>\n<h2>Watchfulness and prayer</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:2-Col4:3\">COL 4:2–4:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:41\">MAT 26:41</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:38\">MRK 14:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:33\">MRK 13:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:36\">LUK 21:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:18\">EPH 6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:7\">1PE 4:7</a></p>\n<h2>Watchfulness for the return of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:42-Matt24:44\">MAT 24:42–24:44</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:1-Matt25:13\">MAT 25:1–25:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:32-Mark13:37\">MRK 13:32–13:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:35-Luke12:40\">LUK 12:35–12:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:32-Luke21:36\">LUK 21:32–21:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:4-1Thess5:8\">1TH 5:4–5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:15\">REV 16:15</a></p>\n<h2>Watchfulness for opportunities to serve the Lord</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:15\">1PE 3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:15-Eph5:16\">EPH 5:15–5:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:5-Col4:6\">COL 4:5–4:6</a></p>\n<h3>Meeting the needs of others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:18\">EPH 6:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:36-Matt26:40\">MAT 26:36–26:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:10\">GAL 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:1\">TIT 3:1</a></p>\n<h2>Contrast with the watchfulness of unbelievers with evil intent</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:32\">PSA 37:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:9\">1SA 18:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:11\">1SA 19:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:8\">PSA 10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:10\">JER 20:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:16\">MAT 26:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:2\">MRK 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:24\">ACT 9:24</a></p>\n<h2>Warning against neglect of watchfulness</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:2-Rev3:3\">REV 3:2–3:3</a></p>",
